  "text": "Our data showed that the 1 year survival did not differ signifi cantly between patients with or without micrometastasis; however, previous studies in this fi led with longer follow-up time showed that the 10 year survival rate is signifi cantly higher in patients without hepatic micrometastasis in comparison with patients with hepatic micrometastasis. [CITATION_1] Our study also had some limitations on the sample size and the time of follow-up, we suggest to perform following researches in this fi eld with larger sample sizes to fi nd clinicopathologic characteristic which correlate with hepatic micrometastasis.",
